<b>iHCM</b>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p>Today, DIGINFO's flagship human capital management software solution -- DIGINFO iHCM -- sails high in several top Philippine companies such as Dole Philippines Stanfilco Division, Texas Instruments, Bank of Commerce, Unilab, Ramcar Food Group, among others.</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p>DIGINFO iHMC has revolutionized the way companies deliver their HR and payroll services to employees and officers by orchestrating, in a paperless way, the flow of data, information, knowledge and intelligence among the people through a web-based self-service platform.<p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p>DIGINFO iHCM, which consist of the PeopleWARE applications running on BOS/e, iBOS/e and mBOS/e platforms, fully automates the tedious administrative efforts in recruitment, personnel movements management, HR databank management, work schedule management, attendance processing, leave management, and payroll processing. It also simplifies HR strategic efforts in training and development, career management, performance management, employee relations, and competency profiling.</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<b>iMACHINE</b>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p>iMACHINE, DIGINFO's latest innovation, is meant to simplify company IT and cut down upfront and long-term costs while providing cutting-edge private cloud computing functionality.</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p>iMACHINE puts the owners and managers at the front seat of the company operations where ever they may be using their iPad, iPhone, Android or the upcoming Surface.</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p>iMACHINE is an all-in-one system solution consisting of hardware + software + appware + talentware. The hardware could be a high-powered commodity server or a branded one like an IBM, Dell or HP server. The software consists of LAMP components i.e. Linux, Apache, MySQL, PhP, or, if budget permits, it will comprise of an IBM stack e.g. DB2, LotusDomino, etc, or Microsoft stack e.g. Windows, SQL Server, Exchange, etc., or Oracle stack e.g. DB, etc. The appware is comprised of DIGINFO iTechnology platforms such as BOS/e, iBOS/e and mBOS/e and their respective suites of business applications such as BOS/e Business Engine, iBOS/e WebShell, etc. The talentware is delivered by DIGINFO Consulting and DIGINFO Academy.</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p>What makes iMACHINE unique is iBOS/e 2012, which provides the private cloud platform for business portal, work flow automation, business social, business apps, plus a lot more in Web 2.0 user experience.</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p>iMACHINE comes in different business solution-oriented models such as iMACHINE + iStaffing for manpower services, iMACHINE + iFR for restaurant chains, and iMACHINE + iLegal for legal firms.</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p>DIGINFO Consulting integrates all these hardware + software + appware components and configures and maps them with any 3rd party application such as an ERP thus delivering a total IT solution like no other.</p>
